Coravin, Inc.: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 28, 2017 6:16 AM ET
Machinery

Company Overview of Coravin, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Coravin, Inc. designs and markets wine access systems for wine enthusiasts, restaurants, wine stores, and wineries. Its system allows users to access and pour their favorite wines by the glass without pulling the cork. It also offers wine access needles, triggers, capsules, clamps, needle assortment kits, carry cases, vintage needles, faster pour needles, standard replacement needles, wine bottle sleeve on bottle, wine bottle sleeve with window on bottle, magnum bottle window sleeve on bottle, and replacement base products. The company was incorporated in 2011 and is based in Burlington, Massachusetts.


3 Van de Graaff DriveSuite 101Burlington, MA 01803United StatesFounded in 2011



Phone: 508-655-2739

Fax: 855-692-6728

www.coravin.com







