Coravin, Inc. Key Developments

Coravin, Inc. Expands Availability of Revolutionary Wine Systems
Oct 18 16
Coravin, Inc. has announced expanded availability of the Coravin Wine System in more than 500 Bed Bath & Beyond stores and online, providing a growing number of wine lovers with access to their favorite wines without ever removing the cork. Shoppers can find the Coravin System online and in stores throughout the United States. Shoppers can expect to find a range of options at Bed Bath & Beyond, as the retailer will be carrying both the brand new Coravin Model One and the Coravin Model Two. Both Systems utilize proprietary Coravin technology to access wine and deliver best-in-class wine preservation. The friendly and functional Coravin Model One, priced at $199.95, features a lightweight and durable plastic body with bright soft touch grips. Model Two, a modern and elegant System in brushed graphite with metal accents, is available for $299.95.


CORAVIN™ Expands Availability of Revolutionary Wine Systems in More Than 500 Bed Bath & Beyond Stores
Oct 18 16
CORAVIN™, Inc. announced expanded availability of the Coravin Wine System in more than 500 Bed Bath & Beyond stores and online, providing a growing number of wine lovers with access to their favorite wines without ever removing the cork. Shoppers can find the Coravin System online and in stores throughout the United States. Coravin, which just celebrated its third anniversary, provides users with a unique way to not only taste wine - but also share, compare and explore each glass like never before. The System gives wine enthusiasts the freedom to drink the wines they want while eliminating the pressure to finish a bottle of wine or pour unfinished wine down the drain. Shoppers can expect to find a range of options at Bed Bath & Beyond, as the retailer will be carrying both the brand new Coravin Model One and the Coravin Model Two. Both Systems utilize proprietary Coravin technology to access wine and deliver best-in-class wine preservation. The friendly and functional Coravin Model One, priced at $199.95, features a lightweight and durable plastic body with bright soft touch grips. Model Two, a modern and elegant System in brushed graphite with metal accents, is available for $299.95.


Coravin, Inc. Announces the Appointment of Yvethe Tyszka as Vice President of Marketing
Aug 24 16
CORAVIN, Inc. announced it has named Yvethe Tyszka as Vice President of Marketing to oversee the company’s marketing and communications initiatives, while leading expansion of its global strategy and footprint. Tyszka brings more than 20 years of experience working with countless notable CPG and Durable businesses and brands, including Black & Decker Appliances, Keurig Premium Coffee Systems and Nestle, among others. Most recently, Tyszka was Director of Marketing at Jarden Consumer Solutions.


