ENJOY A FREE 1-YEAR SUBSCRIPTIONTO WINE SPECTATOR MAGAZINE!While supplies last, receive a 1-year subscriptionto Wine Spectator magazine ($89 value, 15 issues).


Current subscribers' subscriptions will automatically be extended by one year.  Please allow 8-10 weeks for delivery of your first issue.  Your acceptance of this offer authorizes us to provide the publisher with your name and postal mailing address for fulfillment of the magazine.  Accepted magazine offer may result in a request for qualifying purchase verification from an independent publishing auditing organization.  Offer available for delivery to US addresses only. Limit one subscription/customer/household/year.  Offer valid while supplies last. 

Please note, Coravin is not responsible for the fulfillment of your subscription. All inquiries should be directed to Wine Spectator.  Should you decide to cancel your subscription, it should be done directly with Wine Spectator.  There is no refund available upon cancellation.  If you prefer NOT to receive your FREE subscription please contact Customer Service. 




 




